{"tid":1469812,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我地跟左黑警劇本做","createTime":"2019-08-14T03:10:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T03:38:44.000Z","uid":118988,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8d3bc20013c479e859e5579f0dcd56f2ce96cd71","tid":1469812,"uid":118988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:10:17.000Z","msg":"原諒我智力不足，只能做事後孔明<br />\n但而家睇黑警所有野係有鋪排<br />\n<br />\n1. 臥底一早混入示威者帶領行動逐步升級<br />\n2. 每晚捉幾十人，其實捉果d都係前線理性派，一來最勇果d身手敏捷難捉，二來想保留佢地制造輿論壓力，而且捉左前線理性派，無人勸止過激行為，前線變得更勇武<br />\n3. 第三步特登粗暴捉/槍傷後勤弱質女流，前線個個同生共死義字當頭，黑警蝦女人絶唔會坐視不理，必然更激進，正中下懷<br />\n4. 呢個時候爆臥底事件，等你地草木皆兵，全心捉鬼，喪失理性自然不攻自破<br />\n5. 尋晚機場有黑警落單被圍毆，原本劇本應該係會開真槍做成第一滴血，警察保護自己攞正牌開槍，唔會上身，而犧牲人命後示威者除了報仇外更別無選擇，但好彩可能條黑警良心發現，無開到，反而幫左我地有條退路<br />\n<br />\n各位想保留同政府談判籌碼的兄弟，全祈唔好跟警察劇本走，呢個時候要諗警察最想我地做乜，就偏唔做<br />\n班仆街臥底最想我地組織下一場衝擊，繼續破壞，甚至打傷打死警犬，我地偏偏和平遊行，甚至發起d建設活動，著黑衫做好事，吹咩？<br />\n<br />\n勇武唔係鬼，勿割蓆，認清警犬劇本，勿中計，保留談判籌碼"},{"pid":"44fb7f2d13c1b43ee6ea32a5e82e9d32d065729c","tid":1469812,"uid":118988,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:17:01.000Z","msg":"自推<br />\n我地回復番和理非，4點鐘許sir自然無野講，<br />\n唔駛一個禮拜肯定收皮，講來講去三幅被無人再睇，直接破壞佢嘅功能<br />\n如果我地做番d和平嘅活動，佢直頭幫埋我地宣傳添"},{"pid":"488fa9ab4aa62d22942e18eecf3165aabac0637f","tid":1469812,"uid":118988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:17:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed83d30c04d5bf719271916ac62f4eea2ed49a6f","tid":1469812,"uid":118988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:18:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6e06d918f903474721a7bc459b90759d3355e91","tid":1469812,"uid":118988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:18:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3b3ed742a1d4d2a8d041dc798830d8afb7a2444","tid":1469812,"uid":118988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:19:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52df9d852262723bb776223174cce78fcf78b6e9","tid":1469812,"uid":118988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:19:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75abea2ce456e395016ef5b19f9ed23afda57926","tid":1469812,"uid":118988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:19:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"343a77a5edcb45a3e196df5470687ae015e89d0a","tid":1469812,"uid":300223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:19:52.000Z","msg":"分析正確。<br />\n改進是需要的。"},{"pid":"56f4a85731ef249cd6c5cf5a0e64fcac3f807afa","tid":1469812,"uid":118988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:20:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68b4d489291470ac80b19f0eb69e76de20b3a9cc","tid":1469812,"uid":11143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:20:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f9ed8f2231b7ee4e487a46c9a1f28a7aecd63e4b","tid":1469812,"uid":42250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:20:29.000Z","msg":"黑 警 機 場 拔 槍 指 嚇 示 威 者 ！ 同 你 逐 格 睇 暨 聽 日 文 宣 方 向<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1467801\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1467801</a>"},{"pid":"437b23e75912a1ab8a6d07286fb6e1400a2ce498","tid":1469812,"uid":118988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:21:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75b39a6060104c25e976bbb5c475853429a85f3c","tid":1469812,"uid":118988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:23:51.000Z","msg":"勇武不可能無限升級，前線付出的足夠多了，應該交比和理非接力"},{"pid":"3362d1a07047fd2743b934a942f7590511178362","tid":1469812,"uid":118988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:31:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02e41d6311c001b3974eb9b10fdc939b28db1b10","tid":1469812,"uid":293308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:38:44.000Z","msg":"借個靚位<br />\n<br />\n【緊急號召】教協遊行 呼籲老師支持罷課<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1464307\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1464307</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YN4BGd8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYN4BGd8.jpg&h=294234f2&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}